Transformer → How those embeddings are processed.
LLM → How all these components work together to generate the next token.

Is Modern NLP the same as Deep Learning?
No. NLP is the field that focuses on processing and understanding human language. Modern NLP mainly uses Deep Learning models,
especially Transformers and Large Language Models, to perform NLP tasks more effectively than traditional rule-based or statistical methods.
